definitions.definition: A town and civil parish with a town council in Cumberland , Cumbria , England , previously in Copeland borough ( OS grid ref NY0110 ) .
A suburb of Wallasey , Wirral borough , Merseyside , England ( OS grid ref SJ3192 ) .
A town in Berkshire County , Massachusetts , United States .
A hamlet in Thorhild County , Alberta , Canada .
